page.title: 04WILD LIFE
page.content: WE HAVE LOTS OF WILD LIFE IN OUR BLOCK LIKE DEER.DEER HAVE A CLOVER SHAPE FOOT PRINT.DEER EAT LEAVES OFF TREES AND GRASS.THE MALE DEER HAVE ANTLERS TO WARN OFF ANY PREDATERS.THE FEMALE DEER DO NOT HAVE ANTLERS.THE DEER THAT HAVE GROWN NEW ANTLERS HAVE TO GET THE SKIN OFF.THEY GET IT OFF BY RUBBING THEM ON TREES.WE OFTEN SEE RABBITS ON THE SIDE OF THE ROAD AND IN FIELDS. RABBITS HAVE LONG FRONT TEETH,LONG LEGS,BIG EARS,RABBITS'BABIES ARE BORN BLIND.RABBITS LOSE HEAT WITH THIER EARS.FOXES ARE NOCTURNAL ANIMALS.THEY HUNT AT NIGHT AND SLEEP IN THE DAY AND SO ALTHOUGH WE HAVE SEEN SOME WE DO NOT OFTEN MEET A FOX.THEY HAVE PRICKED UP EARS BUSHY TAILS.THEY BUILD THIER HOMES UNDER TREES.IN OUR AREA WE HAVE LOTS OF BIRDS LIKE SWALLOWS,HOUSE MARTINS,ROBINS,BLUE TITS,THRUSHES, BLACKBIRDS,ETC.
